    Then User enters the BookNow button and it navigates to the Adactin.com - Hotel Booking Confirmation

    Examples:
    |First Name1|Last Name1|Address1|Card No1|Card type1|Expiry Month1|Expiry Year1|CVV1|
    |Tamil|Sts|Bangalore|1891776655412345|AMEX|12|2022|373|
  
